---
description: Best practices for World of Warcraft Lua scripting (version 5.1)
globs: **/*.lua
alwaysApply: false
---
- Use local variables to minimize global namespace pollution
- Implement error handling with pcall() for robust code
- Optimize performance by minimizing table allocations and using weak tables
- Follow WoW API conventions and use appropriate event handlers
- Keep addons modular and use namespaces to avoid conflicts